description: Ikänik Farms, Inc. operates as an integrated cannabis cultivator, producer, distributor, and dispensary operator in California and Colombia. The company offers pharmaceutical grade cannabinoids, decarboxylated flower, finished CBD products, and finished ingredient cannabis oil for scientific and commercial sales. It provides its products under the Ikanik, Essentials, Ronen, and Rations brands. The company is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
